==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mowing
<hw>Mow"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of one who, or
the operation of that which, mows.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Land from which grass is cut; meadow land.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Mowing machine</b></col>, <cd>an agricultural machine
armed with knives or blades for cutting standing grass, etc. It may be
drawn by a horse or horses, or propelled by a powered
engine.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mown</ent>⟦br⟧
